snippet.title: Best VGM 1085 - Vagrant Story - Graylands Incident Climax
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation
Vagrant Story (2000)
Graylands Incident Climax
Hitoshi Sakimoto
